+# Surface Packet — `<artifact-name>`
+
+> Operating rule: **no orphan artifacts.** Every script, function, workflow, dashboard,
+> prompt pack, audit, resolver, or utility gets one of these. Copy this block, fill all
+> 10 fields, keep it next to the artifact. Surface before sprawl.
