+| # | Field | Value |
+|---|-------|-------|
+| 1 | **Name** | `<artifact-name>` |
+| 2 | **Problem solved** | <one sentence: the pain this removes> |
+| 3 | **User / buyer** | <who runs it / who pays for the outcome> |
+| 4 | **Existing artifact path** | `<repo-relative path>` |
+| 5 | **How to run it** | `<exact command(s)>` |
+| 6 | **How to verify it** | <observable signal that it worked> |
+| 7 | **How to disable / uninstall** | <how to stop it / remove it, or "N/A — stateless"> |
+| 8 | **Safety / privacy boundary** | <what it can touch; what it must not; auth needed> |
+| 9 | **Current proof / receipt** | <last successful run, test, or output sample> |
+| 10 | **Packaging level** | L0 internal util · L1 documented command · L2 local UI tile · L3 public demo · L4 sellable offer |
